element.name: Number of Each EMS Personnel Level on Normal 911 Response (Non-Transport) Vehicle
element.definition: The number of each personnel level for your EMS Agency's Medical (Non-911) Non-Transport Ambulance.
element.v3Comment: Indicate the number of each of the following EMS Personnel levels on the crew. Associated with each Certification/Licensure Level in dVehicle.04 (Crew State Certification/Licensure Levels).
